{"tid":967133,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美署理防長履新 叫各軍種部長謹記「中國，中國，中國」","createTime":"2019-01-03T09:38:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-03T10:55:23.000Z","uid":28765,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d7965b7ea9ac206373f0fabeb140daf0030a883e","tid":967133,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T09:38:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190103/large/1546496935_8a96.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190103%2Flarge%2F1546496935_8a96.jpg&h=8e905c1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n元旦履新的美國署理國防部長沙納漢（Patrick Shanahan），與各軍種的部長開會時，提醒他們謹記「中國，中國，中國」，可見他對中國的重視。<br />\n<br />\n沙納漢叫國防部要員着眼於國防戰略報告。該官員沒有闡釋沙納漢的中國觀，但有美國官員透露，沙納漢是國防部對華擺出強硬姿態的幕後推手，而去年美國國防戰略報告將就中俄視為戰略競爭對手。<br />\n<br />\n馬蒂斯（Jim Mattis）上月宣佈辭任防長，總統特朗普委任國防部副部長沙納漢為署理防長。56歲的沙納漢沒有從軍經驗，沒有外交經驗，之前也無當官經驗，只當過波音飛機公司高層。不過，他執行力強，在國防部任職18個月，已交出多項政績，包括協助馬蒂斯把國防戰略重心由反恐轉向遏止中、俄。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190103/59098839\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190103%2F59098839&d=GTD8tfl%2BihbajyS3zzIAvwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=b4b75270\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190103%2F59098839&h=92b49e37\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190103/59098839</a>"},{"pid":"a7dfe5894aac0c9041d875537eca92495ed8da6e","tid":967133,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T10:03:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b43f3c1b4eb69cd5f95b781df0d1e4043dbafde4","tid":967133,"uid":9286,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T10:37:13.000Z","msg":"恐怖分子<br />\n中共&gt;ISIS"},{"pid":"91233954659b90858b584874342e6de5819fc7ed","tid":967133,"uid":53705,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T10:50:37.000Z","msg":"我認為美軍 要學以下三句 普通話<br />\n<br />\n「我們是美軍, 你們投降吧, 可以不死」<br />\n「你們告訴情報給我們美軍, 可以獲得綠卡」<br />\n「你們的財產和家人都放在我們美國, 不投降就被凍結了」<br />\n<br />\n美軍學識呢三句野, 基本上連槍都唔洗帶<br />\n見到中國官員/解放軍 就講出來, 即刻打勝仗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8500d02c7fa56be693e0318bce9a0f7b96aeb555","tid":967133,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T10:55:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}